[B][COLOR=#55AAFF]‚ú® Features[/COLOR][/B]
[LIST]
[*][B]/sie[/B] or [B]/siegui[/B] opens a clean [I]Player List[/I].
[*][B]Left-click[/B]: target inventory (vanilla view; your own inventory is visible at the bottom).
[*][B]Right-click[/B]: [I]Armor/Offhand[/I] (read-only) with a [I]Back[/I] button.
[*][B]Shift-click[/B]: player‚Äôs Ender Chest.
[*][B]Q / Ctrl+Q / Middle-click[/B]: configurable [I]Item Palette[/I] (full stack / single item).
[*][B]Compass icon[/B]: browse stored [I]Offline Players[/I] (inventories, armor/offhand, ender chest).
[*][B]Bucket icon[/B]: toggle [I]Delete Mode[/I] (left-click = delete stack, right-click = minus one).
[*][B]Book icon[/B]: open the multilingual in-game [I]Help Book[/I] (English & German).
[*]Optional [I]Back on close[/I]: after ESC/E, return to the player list.
[*]No web UI, no extra ports ‚Äì everything in-game. Only [ICODE]sie.use[/ICODE] required.
[/LIST]

