[B][COLOR=#55AAFF]Installation[/COLOR][/B]
[LIST=1]
[*]Put [ICODE]SimpleInventarEdit-<version>.jar[/ICODE] into [ICODE]plugins/[/ICODE].
[*]Start the server (creates [ICODE]plugins/SimpleInventarEdit/config.yml[/ICODE]).
[*](Optional) Adjust [I]Back on close[/I] & the [I]Palette[/I].
[*]Grant permission (e.g., with LuckPerms):
[CODE]lp user <YourName> permission set sie.use true[/CODE]
[*]In game: [ICODE]/sie[/ICODE] [ICODE]/siegui[/ICODE]
[/LIST]

[B][COLOR=#55AAFF]Toolbar Cheatsheet[/COLOR][/B]
